[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    426[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # --- Acuity Pattern Library ---
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    427[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Red-flag clinical patterns owned by the patient-safety
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    428[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # committee. Each pattern has a triggering condition, a routing
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    429[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # target, and a severity. Production stores this as a versioned
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    430[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # artifact with named clinical-leadership ownership and a
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    431[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # quarterly review cadence; the dict below is illustrative.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    432[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ACUITY_PATTERN_LIBRARY = {
