[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Step 7: Administer Screeners with Validated Wordings
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m *The pseudocode calls this `administer_screener_bundle(session_id, bundle)`. Screeners are not paraphrased. The bot administers the validated wording, captures the response in the validated response set, computes the score per the validated rules, and writes the score plus item-level responses to the session findings. PHQ-9 item 9 (and equivalent crisis-sensitive items) route to the crisis pipeline through the screener path.*
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def screener_administer_tool_capture_item(
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         screener_id: str,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         item_id: Optional[str],
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         answer_text: str,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         language: str) -> dict:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Capture a screener-item response in the validated response
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     set. Returns ask_clarification if the response cannot be
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     matched to a valid option; routes to the crisis pipeline if
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     the item is crisis-sensitive and the response value is in
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     the configured crisis range.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     screener = SCREENER_LIBRARY.get(screener_id, {})
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     items = screener.get("items", [])
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     if not items:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         return {"action": "no_capture", "finding": None}
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     item = None
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     if item_id:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         item = next(
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             (i for i in items if i.get("id") == item_id),
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             None)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     else:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # When no item_id is provided, default to the first
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # item. Production tracks per-screener item progress
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # explicitly; the demo administers one item per turn.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         item = items[0]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     if not item:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         return {"action": "no_capture", "finding": None}
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     response_value = _match_response_value(
